<h2 id="using-the-highlight-box">Using the highlight box</h2>

<p>The highlight box should display important information to a user after completing a transaction. It will usually be on the final page of a <a href="/docs/core/elements/form">form</a>.</p>

<p>A <code>h1</code> tag is included within Hilight-box, and so should be the page heading where this is used, or if this is not the case to be swapped out for the class <code>.page-heading</code></p>
